  <Sequence sap2010:Annotation.AnnotationText="This simple workflow returns the most recent addded file in the folder based on date and time in a descending order. It ignores the file type and it returns one file.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;If you want to return more files:&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;inside the second assigne (GettingFile). change the number inside the last paranthesis from 1 to the number of files you want.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;to only return files of type eg .pfd or .png etc:&#xD;&#xA;replace the wild card &quot;*&quot; with the extension e.g &quot;.img&quot;&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA; " sap:VirtualizedContainerService.HintSize="304,355.2" sap2010:WorkflowViewState.IdRef="Sequence_1">
